name: SecreD - Foot Art
description:
Warning this game contains nudity.



Solve sliding puzzle. Take photos of female models for your magazine. So it be published on time. Relax with anime-girls.
SecreD is a sliding puzzle game. There are 30 levels and the difficulty level increases in every 10 levels. Moves are limited. You must finish the level before you run out of moves.But it still a relaxing game.
